# Available Capabilities (condensed)

Per-server tool reference. **Optional: enable for your workflow.** Add rows for your project's MCP servers.

| Server | Tools |
|--------|-------|
| harness | run_terminal_cmd → scripts (copy_continue_prompt, sanitize_input, validate_handoff_scp) |
| git | status, diff, log, commit, push, pull |
| scp | scp_inspect, scp_sanitize, scp_contain, scp_quarantine, scp_validate_output, scp_run_pipeline |
| context7 | resolve-library-id, query-docs (library documentation) |

**Extend:** Add your MCP servers (browser, sqlite, docker, etc.) to this table. See harness docs for integration.